<item>
            <title>[LU-10270] remove a early rx code from o2ib lnd</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10270</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;early RX added to the o2ib lnd as attempt to reordering problem handling. when messages have arrived before actual connection sets. But it code can fill all incoming queue and normal connect will not processed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lets remove it code as have no real reasons to have it and data will be from stale connect likely.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
